    public final class StackMapTable
extends org.apache.bcel.classfile.Attribute
    This class represents a stack map attribute used for preverification of Java classes for the Java 2 Micro Edition (J2ME). This attribute is used by the KVM and contained within the Code attribute of a method. See CLDC specification ï¿½5.3.1.2
